The mission of the Society for Scholarly Publishing (SSP) is "[t]o advance scholarly publishing and communication, and the professional development of its members through education, collaboration, and networking." SSP established <em><strong>The Scholarly Kitchen</strong></em> blog in February 2008 to keep SSP members and interested parties aware of new developments in publishing.<br> 
